9.8% v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p trong 8 n\u0103m (C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3: sau khi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n, m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng A ph\u1ea3i thanh to\u00e1n t\u1ea7m l\u00e3i + g\u1ed1c = 8Tr v\u00e0 bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 theo quy t\u1eafc tr\u1eeb l\u00f9i t\u1ea7m 4,6Tr VN\u0110 .<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mua xe Kia tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 95% gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb xe, th\u1eddi gian vay t\u1ed1i \u0111a 7 n\u0103m. Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nhanh g\u1ecdn, th\u1eddi gian th\u1ea9m duy\u1ec7t trong v\u00f2ng 24h, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u1edf t\u1ec9nh, bao \u0111\u1eadu h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 kh\u00f3. Vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-665673789\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f170-o1\" lang=\"vi\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"><\/p> <ul><\/ul><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/279#wpcf7-f170-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form init\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" data-status=\"init\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"170\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"5.6.4\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"vi\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f170-o1\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container_post\" value=\"0\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_posted_data_hash\" value=\"\" \/>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-yeu-cau\">\n<div class=\"form-tieu-de\">\n<h3>Y\u00caU C\u1ea6U B\u00c1O GI\u00c1<\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \"B\u00c1O GI\u00c1 \u